Multiple people have sustained injuries in an accident involving a bus and a bakkie. The accident happened on the N2 Kwambonambi Bridge. Reports from paramedics say that the injuries range from mild to serious. Emergency vehicles, fire, police and rescue services are on the scene of the accident to attend to the injured. The total number of patients has yet to be confirmed, once treated the patients will be moved to a medical facility for further assessment and care, this is a developing story. For more see tweet below: 